---
import '../styles/global.css';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | Ads Calculator';
const description = 'Privacy Policy of Ads Calculator. Learn how we handle your data, cookies, and compliance with GDPR and Google AdSense policies.';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://adsroicalc.com/privacy" />
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8428748101355923" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-4 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="font-bold text-xl">Ads <span class="text-blue-600 italic">Calculator</span></a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline">← Back to calculator</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p>Ads Calculator (<strong>adsroicalc.com</strong>) is a free online tool designed to help marketers and business owners calculate ROAS, ROI, and breakeven points for their advertising campaigns. We are committed to protecting your privacy.</p>
          <p>For any privacy-related enquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@adsroicalc.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">2. What data we collect</h2>
          <p>Ads Calculator does <strong>not collect, store, or transmit any personal data</strong> entered into the calculator. All calculations are performed locally in your browser.</p>
          <p>However, we do use third-party services that may collect anonymous usage data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong>: Collects anonymized data about page visits, session duration, and general geographic location. No personally identifiable information (PII) is recorded.</li>
            <li><strong>Google Tag Manager</strong>: Used to manage analytics scripts on our site.</li>
            <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong>: We participate in the Google AdSense program, which displays advertisements on our site. Google may use cookies to show you relevant ads based on your browsing history.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong>: Google Analytics uses cookies to track anonymous usage statistics.</li>
            <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong>: Google AdSense uses cookies to display personalized advertisements. You can opt out of personalized advertising at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">adssettings.google.com</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can manage cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may reduce site functionality.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">4. Google AdSense and Third-Party Advertising</h2>
          <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
          <p>You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.aboutads.info/choices/</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>If you are located in the European Economic Area, you have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Right to access any personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Right to erasure of your data.</li>
            <li>Right to restrict or object to processing.</li>
            <li>Right to data portability.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@adsroicalc.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">6. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this page periodically. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-8 px-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p>© 2026 Ads Calculator. All rights reserved. |
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="/legal" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Legal Notice</a> |
        <a href="/cookies" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Cookie Policy</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
